Description: The Bachelor of Divinity (BD) is our central award. It is a four-year degree designed for men and women who want a biblical and theological foundation to prepare them for a lifetime of service in full time Christian ministry.
The Bachelor of Theology (BTh) is designed for men and women who want a biblical and theological foundation to prepare them for a lifetime of service in Christian ministry.

Course: Advanced Diploma of Bible, Mission and Ministry
Description: The Advanced Diploma is a flexible, accredited, 1 year course that prepares you to serve Jesus in any place.
The Master of Arts (Theology) program is aimed at providing continuing education in theology for graduates in full-time ministry.
A Master of Theology (MTh) is a postgraduate research award and is aimed at specifically equipping graduates for future teaching ministries.

The Doctor of Philosophy (PhD) aims to equip qualified persons for a vocation of teaching and research in theological colleges and universities and for the scholarly enhancement of Christian ministry.
The Diploma of Biblical Theology breaks geographical boundaries to teach and equip you to serve the Lord wherever you are.
